task.summary: + Die, Board, Game, Square, Money, Player and Main classes are created. + In every turn every user rolls dice + In every turn every can go to the square that corresponds to their current dice values. + In every turn, every user's current situation is displayed in console.
+ Class "TaxAdministration" added. + Class "Transaction" added. + We can increase and decrease players money.
+ Renting the already rented squares are forbidden now. + Tax Administration squares added. + Sale price is double of the renting price.
+ Can't rent or buy any property that you already have. + Output messages shaped into a new way. + Square traverse is now circle.
+Edits on Game Class +Winner established +First iteration ended
